Sum= 2/9 [(10^1 - 1) + (10^2 - 1) + ( 10^3 - 1) +…… + (10^n-1)]

Sum= 2/9 [(10 + 10^2 + 10^ 3 + 10^4 + …) - ( 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1 + 1….n 1’s)

Sum=2/9 [ {10 × (10^n - 1) / (10 -1)} - n]

Sum= 2/9 [ {10 × (10^n - 1) / 9} - n]

sum=2/9*[(10n-1-9n)/9]


